Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n实现 Valkey 存储后端，包括:\n- `ValkeyStore` 结构实现 Store 接口\n- Valkey 配置管理\n- Session 序列化/反序列化\n- 错误处理\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-014/spec.md","time":{"start":1775859098148,"end":1775859098179}}}}
