- DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n45:   - ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)\n46:   - ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)\n47:   - UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)\n48:   - Close()\n49:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n50: \n51: ### Phase 3: Unit Tests\n52: \n53: - [ ] **T3.1** Create `pkg/store/valkey_test.go` - Test Setup\n54:   - Create test helpers\n55:   - Create mock valkey.Client\n56:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n57: \n58: - [ ] **T3.2** Test CRUD operations\n59:   - Test Get/Store/Update/Delete\n60:   - Test ErrNotFound handling\n61:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n62: \n63: - [ ] **T3.3** Test ZSET index operations\n64:   - Test ListExpiredSandboxes\n65:   - Test ListInactiveSandboxes\n66:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n67: \n68: ### Phase 4: Validation\n69: \n70: - [ ] **T4.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n71: - [ ] **T4.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n72: - [ ] **T4.3** Verify test coverage ≥ 80%\n73: - [ ] **T4.4** Run tests with race detector\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## Acceptance Criteria\n78: \n79: - [ ] ValkeyStore 完整实现 Store 接口\n80: - [ ] 支持环境变量配置\n81: - [ ] ZSET 索引正确维护\n82: - [ ] 错误处理完善\n83: - [ ] Pass `go vet`\n84: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint`\n85: - [ ] Test coverage ≥ 80%\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## Notes\n90: \n91: - 参考 AR-013 Redis 实现的 API 设计\n92: - 使用 valkey-go 的 B() builder 模式构建命令\n93: - DoMulti 用于原子操作\n\n(End of file - total 93 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-1 pending] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Dependencies Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add Valkey client dependency\n  - Run: `go get github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go@latest`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes